Hi Monika, 

As per our telephonic conversation, I am enclosing the JD for your
reference. Kindly go through it and let me know. 

Job Description:- 

The selected candidate will be making calls to the numbers provided to
them and describing them about the service/products of the company. The
Candidate needs to be good in convincing people and encouraging them to
sign up with us, dealing diplomatically and responding to their queries.
She will be working independently and will report directly to the
director.

This is a office job and doesn't require travelling. The office timings
will be from 10:30 am to 6:00 pm.

About the Company:- 

SIMPLIFYTRIPS.COM is an upcoming start-up aimed to revolutionize the
travel domain. It is one of its kind platform where you can excel your
skills manifold. Its presence is all over India. For more details you
can visit www.simplifytrips.com [1]

If you think that this job is not suitable for you then kindly forward
this mail in your reference to the one in need. 

